            any_country = {
			        limit = {
				        government = absolute_empire
				        has_country_flag = dynamic_loc
			        }
			        THIS = {
                        any_country = { limit = { has_country_flag = dynamic_loc tag = REB } slots = { limit = { has_province_modifier = dynamic_loc } secede_province = THIS state_scope = { change_region_name = "Rebel" } secede_province = QQQ } }
